author: dgraham
msg: Added a getProcessorForModule() method that won't create a
RequestProcessor when one doesn't exist.  Call this method from
destroyModules() instead of getRequestProcessor() for PR# 21337.

author: dgraham
msg: Reverse if logic to continue to next loop iteration in destroyModules()
to prevent a large block of code being nested in the if.

author: dgraham
msg: Added scriptLanguage property to the form and javascript tags for PR# 17234.
This property is ignored in XHTML mode but allows developers to turn off
the "language" attribute of <script> tags in HTML.
